<h2><a href="/en/component/content/89-faculty-resources/334-program-evaluation" mce_href="/en/component/content/89-faculty-resources/334-program-evaluation">Program Evaluation</a></h2>
Based on a general province-wide policy, Concordia has developed appraisal guidelines specific to the needs of its University community. All information on the process, links and required reference material can be found within the JMSB Program Evaluation folder.<br /><br />We hope this website will help you to easily access information relating to the key functions of our office and we invite you to bookmark this page.-->
