<h2 class="rightrail_heading"><br />Position Announcements</h2>
<b>Limited-term Lecturer (Department of Management)<br /> </b>Concordia
 University's John Molson School of Business is inviting applicants for a
 limited-term Lecturer appointment in Management to begin January 3rd, 
2012.<strong> </strong>The application deadline is November 25, 2011. <a title="Call for applications - limited-term Lecturer (Department of Management)" href="http://johnmolson.concordia.ca/en/faculty-research/departments/management/position-announcement">Read more</a>...<br /><br /><b>Finance Positions Available<br /></b>The Department of Finance is seeking, 
subject to budgetary approval, qualified applicants for tenure-track and
 visiting positions starting July 1, 2012. The application deadline is December 1, 2011. <a title="Tenure-track and visiting positions in Finance" href="http://johnmolson.concordia.ca/en/faculty-research/departments/finance/position-announcement">Read more</a>...<br /><b><br />Accountancy Positions Available<br /> </b>The Department of Accountancy invites applications for two tenure-track positions in the department of Accountancy. The application deadline is December 1, 2011. <a title="Department of Accoutancy - Tenure-track positions" href="http://johnmolson.concordia.ca/en/faculty-research/departments/accountancy/position-announcements">Read more</a>...<b><br /> </b><br /><br />
